== Keywording and unmasking ==

To assist users with stable systems and those who which to test specific package versions, the overlay provides a set of {{Path|package.accept_keywords}}, {{Path|package.mask}}, and {{Path|package.unmask}} files. All available files are in the [https://gitweb.gentoo.org/proj/kde.git/tree/Documentation Documentation] directory.

For example, to keyword KDE Frameworks 5 master branch: 
{{RootCmd|cd /etc/portage/package.accept_keywords|
  |ln -s /path/to/overlay/kde/Documentation/package.accept_keywords/kde-frameworks-live.keywords}}

